tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE experimental_data (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_name VARCHAR(50),
    hypothesis VARCHAR(255),
    test_group VARCHAR(10),
    data_value FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE hypothesis_testing_data (
    experiment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_name VARCHAR(255),
    experiment_description TEXT,
    experiment_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE hypothesis_results (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_id INT,
    metric_name VARCHAR(255),
    metric_value DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE ab_testing_data (
    test_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    test_name VARCHAR(255),
    test_description TEXT,
    test_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE ab_testing_results (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    test_id INT,
    metric_name VARCHAR(255),
    metric_value DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE experimental_parameters (
    parameter_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    parameter_name VARCHAR(255),
    parameter_description TEXT,
    parameter_type VARCHAR(50)
)
